hadiths[23]{hadithnumber,text}:
5862,"Rooh-bin-Ubada ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : maine Hisham-bin-Zaid se suna, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo hadis bayan kar rahe they ke aik Yahudi aurat ne gosht mein zahar mila diya aur phir us ( gosht ( ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas ley aai , jis tarah Khalid (bin-Haaris) ki hadis hai."
5863,"Rooh-bin-Ubada ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : maine Hisham-bin-Zaid se suna, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo hadis bayan kar rahe they ke aik Yahudi aurat ne gosht mein zahar mila diya aur phir us ( gosht ( ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas ley aai , jis tarah Khalid (bin-Haaris) ki hadis hai."
5864,"Jarir ne Aamash se, unhon-ne abu-Zuhaa se, unhon-ne Masruq se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, kaha : jab ham mein se koi shakhs bimar hota to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us (ke mutaassira hissey) par apna dayan hath phertey, phir farmatey : takleef ko door kar de, aey tamam insanon ke paalne waley ! shifa de, tu hi shifa dene wala hai, teri shifa ke siwa koi shifa nahi, aisi shifa jo bimari ko (zarra barabar baqi) nahi chhodti. phir jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bimar huey aur aap ke liye aaza ko harkat dena mushkil ho gaya to maine aap ka hath thaamaa taake jis tarah khud Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kiya kartey they, mein bhi isi tarah karun to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apna hath mere hath se chhuda liya, phir farmaya : aey mere Allah ! mujhey bakhsh de aur mujhey rafeeq aalaa ki maiyat (sath) ata kar de. unhon-ne kaha : phir main dekhney lagi to aap wafaat farma chukey they."
5865,"Jarir ne Aamash se, unhon-ne abu-Zuhaa se, unhon-ne Masruq se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, kaha : jab ham mein se koi shakhs bimar hota to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us (ke mutaassira hissey) par apna dayan hath phertey, phir farmatey : takleef ko door kar de, aey tamam insanon ke paalne waley ! shifa de, tu hi shifa dene wala hai, teri shifa ke siwa koi shifa nahi, aisi shifa jo bimari ko (zarra barabar baqi) nahi chhodti. phir jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bimar huey aur aap ke liye aaza ko harkat dena mushkil ho gaya to maine aap ka hath thaamaa taake jis tarah khud Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kiya kartey they, mein bhi isi tarah karun to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apna hath mere hath se chhuda liya, phir farmaya : aey mere Allah ! mujhey bakhsh de aur mujhey rafeeq aalaa ki maiyat (sath) ata kar de. unhon-ne kaha : phir main dekhney lagi to aap wafaat farma chukey they."
5866,"Yahya-bin-Yahya ne kaha : hamein Hushaim ne khabar di, Abu-Bakar-bin-khallaad aur abu-Kuraib ne kaha : hamein abu-Muawiya ne hadis bayan ki, Bishr-bin-Khalid ne kaha : hamein Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne hadis sunai. ibne-Bashar ne kaha : hamein ibne-Adi ne hadis bayan ki, un donon ( Muhammad-bin-Jafar aur ibne-abi-Adi) ne Shoba se riwayat ki. (usi tarah) abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba aur Abu-Bakar-bin-khallaad ne bhi hamein ye hadis bayan ki, donon ne kaha : hamein Yahya qattaan ne Sufiyan se hadis bayan ki, un sab ne Jarir ki sanad ke sath Aamash se riwayat ki. Hushaim aur Shoba ki riwayat mein hai ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apna hath us ( mutaassira hissey ( par phertey aur) Sufiyan ( Sory ki hadis mein hai : aap apna dayan hath is par phertey aur Aamash se Sufiyan aur unse Yahya ki riwayat ki hui hadis ke aakhir mein hai, kaha : maine Mansoor ko ye hadis sunai to unhon-ne usi ke mutabiq Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se Masruq aur unse Ibrahim ki riwayat ki hui hadis bayan ki."
5867,"Yahya-bin-Yahya ne kaha : hamein Hushaim ne khabar di, Abu-Bakar-bin-khallaad aur abu-Kuraib ne kaha : hamein abu-Muawiya ne hadis bayan ki, Bishr-bin-Khalid ne kaha : hamein Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne hadis sunai. ibne-Bashar ne kaha : hamein ibne-Adi ne hadis bayan ki, un donon ( Muhammad-bin-Jafar aur ibne-abi-Adi) ne Shoba se riwayat ki. (usi tarah) abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba aur Abu-Bakar-bin-khallaad ne bhi hamein ye hadis bayan ki, donon ne kaha : hamein Yahya qattaan ne Sufiyan se hadis bayan ki, un sab ne Jarir ki sanad ke sath Aamash se riwayat ki. Hushaim aur Shoba ki riwayat mein hai ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apna hath us ( mutaassira hissey ( par phertey aur) Sufiyan ( Sory ki hadis mein hai : aap apna dayan hath is par phertey aur Aamash se Sufiyan aur unse Yahya ki riwayat ki hui hadis ke aakhir mein hai, kaha : maine Mansoor ko ye hadis sunai to unhon-ne usi ke mutabiq Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se Masruq aur unse Ibrahim ki riwayat ki hui hadis bayan ki."
5868,"abu-Awana ne Mansoor se, unhon-ne Ibrahim se, unhon-ne Masruq se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke bila shubah Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab kisi mareez ki iyaadat kartey they, to farmatey : takleef door kar de, aey sab logon ke paalne waley ! isko shifa ata kar, to shifa dene wala hai, teri shifa ke siwa koi shifa nahi, aisi shifa (de) jo (zarra barabar) bimari ko na chhodey."
5869,"abu-Awana ne Mansoor se, unhon-ne Ibrahim se, unhon-ne Masruq se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke bila shubah Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab kisi mareez ki iyaadat kartey they, to farmatey : takleef door kar de, aey sab logon ke paalne waley ! isko shifa ata kar, to shifa dene wala hai, teri shifa ke siwa koi shifa nahi, aisi shifa (de) jo (zarra barabar) bimari ko na chhodey."
5870,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba aur Zuhair-bin-Harab ne kaha : hamein Jarir ne Mansoor se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne abu-zuhaa se, unhon-ne Masruq se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab kisi mareez ke paas tashrif latey to us ke liye dua farmatey huey kehtey : takleef door kar de, aey sab insanon ke paalne waley ! aur shifa ata kar, tu hi shifa dene wala hai, shifa ata kar, teri shifa ke siwa (kahin) koi shifa nahi, aisi shifa se jo bimari ko (baqi) na chhodey Abu-Bakar ( ibne-Abi-Sheba ( ki riwayat mein hai : aap uske liye dua farmatey aur kehtey : aur tu hi shifa dene wala hai."
5871,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba aur Zuhair-bin-Harab ne kaha : hamein Jarir ne Mansoor se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne abu-zuhaa se, unhon-ne Masruq se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab kisi mareez ke paas tashrif latey to us ke liye dua farmatey huey kehtey : takleef door kar de, aey sab insanon ke paalne waley ! aur shifa ata kar, tu hi shifa dene wala hai, shifa ata kar, teri shifa ke siwa (kahin) koi shifa nahi, aisi shifa se jo bimari ko (baqi) na chhodey Abu-Bakar ( ibne-Abi-Sheba ( ki riwayat mein hai : aap uske liye dua farmatey aur kehtey : aur tu hi shifa dene wala hai."
5872,"Israel ne Mansoor se, unhon-ne Ibrahim aur Muslim-bin-sabeeh se, unhon-ne Masruq se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (jab kisi mareez ki iyaadat kartey ( they ( aagey ( jis tarah abu-Awana aur Jarir ki hadis mein hai."
5873,"Israel ne Mansoor se, unhon-ne Ibrahim aur Muslim-bin-sabeeh se, unhon-ne Masruq se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (jab kisi mareez ki iyaadat kartey ( they ( aagey ( jis tarah abu-Awana aur Jarir ki hadis mein hai."
5874,"ibne-Numair ne kaha : hamein Hisham ne apne walid se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) un kalimaat ke sath dam kartey they : takleef door farma de, aey sab insanon ke paalne waley ! shifa terey hi hath mein hai, terey siwa is takleef ko door karne wala aur koi nahi."
5875,"ibne-Numair ne kaha : hamein Hisham ne apne walid se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) un kalimaat ke sath dam kartey they : takleef door farma de, aey sab insanon ke paalne waley ! shifa terey hi hath mein hai, terey siwa is takleef ko door karne wala aur koi nahi."
5876,abu-Usama aur Esa-bin-Yonus donon ne Hisham se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah riwayat ki.
5877,abu-Usama aur Esa-bin-Yonus donon ne Hisham se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah riwayat ki.
5878,"Suraij-bin-Yoonus aur Yahya-bin-Ayub ne kaha : hamein Ibad-bin-Ibad ne Hisham-bin-Urwa se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, kaha : jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ghar walon mein se koi bimar hota to aap panah dilwaaney waley kalimaat is par phoonktey. phir jab aap us marz mein mubtala huey jis mein aap ki wafaat hui to maine aap par phoonknaa aur aap ka apna hath aap ke jism Mubarak par phernaa shuru kar diya kyonke aap ka hath mere hath se zyada ba-barkat tha. Yahya-bin-Ayub ki riwayat mein ((بِالْمَعَوِّذَاتِ) ke bajaey) ( بمَعَوِّذَاتِ ( ) panah dilwaaney waley kuchh kalimaat ( hain."
5879,"Suraij-bin-Yoonus aur Yahya-bin-Ayub ne kaha : hamein Ibad-bin-Ibad ne Hisham-bin-Urwa se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, kaha : jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ghar walon mein se koi bimar hota to aap panah dilwaaney waley kalimaat is par phoonktey. phir jab aap us marz mein mubtala huey jis mein aap ki wafaat hui to maine aap par phoonknaa aur aap ka apna hath aap ke jism Mubarak par phernaa shuru kar diya kyonke aap ka hath mere hath se zyada ba-barkat tha. Yahya-bin-Ayub ki riwayat mein ((بِالْمَعَوِّذَاتِ) ke bajaey) ( بمَعَوِّذَاتِ ( ) panah dilwaaney waley kuchh kalimaat ( hain."
5880,"Malik ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne Urwa se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, ke jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bimar hotey to aap khud par muawwizaat ( muawwizatain aur doosrey panah dilwaaney wali duaein aur aayatein ( padhtey aur phoonk maartey. jab aap ki takleef shadeed ho gaee to main aap par padhti aur aap ki taraf se main aap ka apna hath uski barkat ki ummeed ke sath (aap ke jism par) pherti."
5881,"Malik ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne Urwa se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, ke jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bimar hotey to aap khud par muawwizaat ( muawwizatain aur doosrey panah dilwaaney wali duaein aur aayatein ( padhtey aur phoonk maartey. jab aap ki takleef shadeed ho gaee to main aap par padhti aur aap ki taraf se main aap ka apna hath uski barkat ki ummeed ke sath (aap ke jism par) pherti."
5882,"Yunus Mamar aur Ziyad sab ne ibne-Shahab se, Imam Malik ki sanad ke sath unki hadis ki tarah hadis bayan ki. Malik ke ilawa aur kisi ki sanad mein aap ke hath ki barkat ki ummeed se ke alfaz nahi. aur Yunus aur Ziyad ki hadis mein hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab bimar hotey to aap khud apne aap par kalimaat ( padh kar) phoonktey aur apne jism par apna hath phertey."
5883,"Yunus Mamar aur Ziyad sab ne ibne-Shahab se, Imam Malik ki sanad ke sath unki hadis ki tarah hadis bayan ki. Malik ke ilawa aur kisi ki sanad mein aap ke hath ki barkat ki ummeed se ke alfaz nahi. aur Yunus aur Ziyad ki hadis mein hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab bimar hotey to aap khud apne aap par kalimaat ( padh kar) phoonktey aur apne jism par apna hath phertey."
5884,"Abdur-Rehman-bin-Aswad ne apne walid se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se dam karne ke barey mein malum kiya to unhon-ne bataya Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Ansar ke aik ghar ke logon ko har zahreeley janwar ke dank se (shifa ke liye) dam karne ki ijazat ata farmai ."
